Intent
----------------------------------------------------------------

This design is shared to support community solidarity and transparency.
The intent of this license is to allow Brown University full freedom to
use the design in service of its community, while preventing commercial
exploitation or misuse by third parties.

This Intent section is explanatory only and does not modify the legal
terms below.

